### 0. Health (no auth)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/health/nomba

### 1. Provision virtual account  (tenant or landlord JWT)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agreements/8b565c14-79f7-4b0d-b84f-19cfbb2b18e8/provision-nomba
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantJwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 2. Payment status BEFORE  (expect reconciliation_status = PENDING)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agreements/8b565c14-79f7-4b0d-b84f-19cfbb2b18e8/payment-status
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantJwt}}

### 3. Webhook FULL payment  (paste body from simulator full_payment)
# Body MUST be the exact JSON the simulator printed for full_payment.
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/webhooks/nomba/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
nomba-signature: 96n8z+rBJ872dk0Ep1+xB/RZoShlwhBwJism6Jcn+Vc=
nomba-timestamp: 2026-07-01T10:00:00Z

### 4. Webhook REPLAY (idempotency -> already_processed)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/webhooks/nomba/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
nomba-signature: {{sigFull}}
nomba-timestamp: {{ts}}

< ./payloads/full_payment.json

### 5. Webhook BAD signature -> 401
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/webhooks/nomba/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
nomba-signature: invalidsignature==
nomba-timestamp: {{ts}}

< ./payloads/full_payment.json

### 6. Webhook UNDERPAYMENT
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/webhooks/nomba/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
nomba-signature: {{sigUnder}}
nomba-timestamp: {{ts}}

< ./payloads/underpayment.json

### 7. Webhook OVERPAYMENT
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/webhooks/nomba/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
nomba-signature: {{sigOver}}
nomba-timestamp: {{ts}}

< ./payloads/overpayment.json

### 8. Webhook MISDIRECTED (unknown agreement)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/webhooks/nomba/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
nomba-signature: {{sigMisdir}}
nomba-timestamp: {{ts}}

< ./payloads/misdirected.json


# @name statusAfter

### 9. Payment status AFTER  (expect FULL_PAYMENT; note transfer_history[0].id)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agreements/8b565c14-79f7-4b0d-b84f-19cfbb2b18e8/payment-status
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantJwt}}

### 10. Lookup + verify landlord bank  (landlord JWT)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/disbursements/lookup-bank
Authorization: Bearer {{landlordJwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "0000000000",
  "bank_code": "035"
}


# @name disburse

### 11. Disburse to landlord  (source_transfer_id auto-pulled from request 9)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agreements/8b565c14-79f7-4b0d-b84f-19cfbb2b18e8/disburse
Authorization: Bearer {{landlordJwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source_transfer_id": "{{statusAfter.response.body.$.transfer_history[0].id}}",
  "retry_count": 0
}

### 12. Disbursement status  (merchant_tx_ref auto-pulled from request 11)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/disbursements/{{disburse.response.body.$.merchant_tx_ref}}
Authorization: Bearer {{landlordJwt}}
